{
  "stem": "21550.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took, and they had to deposit them in a certain place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That we'll be issued cards, like, to get food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And the rations were getting smaller and smaller.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were not big to start with.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they started bringing in people from the little hamlets and little villages around Warsaw, and they dump them all into the city.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So there was a-- a tremendous hunger and a lot of disease.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And people were dying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were dying on the streets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You could see-- you could see children, especially children, you could see after a while, after a few months, you could see skeleton, living skeletons walking the streets.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And you-- you saw them laying on the streets dead, covered with newspapers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was not much we can-- to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We tried-- everybody tried to make a living.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were people who sold their-- who liquidated their businesses before, and they had this cash.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they didn't know what to do with it, because it just was worthless.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was getting-- so they-- they tried to invest it into something, because if somebody had a shoe store and sold his shoes and had accumulated all this-- this money, and there was no replacement.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he tried to-- so my father did a little business by selling them gold.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they had to-- when they needed the money to live, they had to sell this gold.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my father did pretty good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was-- there was no legal activity.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're not-- we're not supposed to do anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're not supposed-- I remember one incident.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father and myself and a friend of his were standing on the street and just talking.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
